    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Wine開啟視窗字體平滑效果]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.renn999.twbbs.org/archives/618"/>
    <updated>2009-12-29T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://www.renn999.twbbs.org/archives/618</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在很早以前用wine的時候只要在user.reg下加入
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>[Software\Wine\X11 Driver]
</span><span class='line'>"ClientSideAntiAliasWithRender"="Y"</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
就可以啟用平滑效果，但是升級到1.1.35之後完全不管用了
因為如果不啟用平滑效果的話，情況會像下圖：
<a href="http://www.renn999.twbbs.org/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Screenshot-Wine-設定.png"><img src="http://www.renn999.twbbs.org/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Screenshot-Wine-設定-283x300.png" alt="" title="Screenshot-Wine 設定" width="283" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-619" /></a></p>

<!--more-->


<p>在網路上已經有真正的解法了，如果您真的很有耐心的話可以看看Wine-Review的<a href="http://www.wine-reviews.net/wine-reviews/tips-n-tricks/how-to-enable-font-anti-aliasing-in-wine.html">這一篇</a>
他有說到將以下的文字存成reg並且匯進去regedit
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>REGEDIT4&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Control Panel\Desktop]
</span><span class='line'>"FontSmoothing"="2"
</span><span class='line'>"FontSmoothingType"=dword:00000002
</span><span class='line'>"FontSmoothingGamma"=dword:00000578
</span><span class='line'>"FontSmoothingOrientation"=dword:00000001</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
但是太麻煩了，最快的方式，打開終端機複製貼上
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>wget http://files.polosatus.ru/winefontssmoothing_en.sh -O- | bash</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
然後，出現以下畫面去作選擇
<a href="http://www.renn999.twbbs.org/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Screenshot-Terminal.png"><img src="http://www.renn999.twbbs.org/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Screenshot-Terminal-300x185.png" alt="" title="Screenshot-Terminal" width="300" height="185" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-621" /></a>
之後可以開啟Wine來看看結果
<a href="http://www.renn999.twbbs.org/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Screenshot-Wine-設定-1.png"><img src="http://www.renn999.twbbs.org/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Screenshot-Wine-設定-1-300x296.png" alt="" title="Screenshot-Wine 設定-1" width="300" height="296" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-620" /></a></p>

<p>這樣看起來棒多了，取代其他字型的regcode</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>[Software\Wine\Fonts\Replacements]
</span><span class='line'>"System"="你要的字型名稱"
</span><span class='line'>"Arial"="你要的字型名稱"
</span><span class='line'>"Fixedsys"="你要的字型名稱"
</span><span class='line'>"Microsoft Sans Serif"="你要的字型名稱"
</span><span class='line'>"MS UI Gothic"="你要的字型名稱"
</span><span class='line'>"Tahoma"="你要的字型名稱"
</span><span class='line'>"Terminal"="你要的字型名稱"
</span><span class='line'>"MingLiU"="你要的字型名稱"
</span><span class='line'>"PMingLiU"="你要的字型名稱"</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>將其附加到user.reg後面即可</p>
]]></content>
